title: la ciudad era nuestra - de stat was von ons - the city was ours
description:
Joost Seelen, 1996, 93 min 

documentary about the squat movement in Holland 1970s to 1980. it is VERY well-made, entirely from interviews and riot footage, and it tells the story of the movement from many points of view.
